# MedVirtual Ad Production

Default priority: **Virtual Medical Admin direct-response ads + animated video** for demo sign-ups.

## Goal
Keep bold VMA static + video ads in the hopper. Make “do this next” obvious for graphics in under two minutes.

## Brand
- Site name: **MedVirtual Ad Production** (not “Creative Handoff” / “Content Doc”)
- Ad-facing: **MedVirtual** only (never MedVirtual.ai)
- Font: Be Vietnam
- Active Meta colors: lime / yellow / cobalt / cyan / vivid green / commercial red / black / white / deep navy / MedVirtual teal
- **No pink** (other buyer territory)

## Service model
Hire dedicated full-time virtual staff who join the practice team.
Not a call center / managed front desk / software / chatbot / AI service.

## Visual DNA
**Current:** High-contrast human-led “Hire a Virtual Medical Admin” — huge headline · generic professional admin · 3–4 benefits · price/trust badges (pending approval) · mobile-first.
Animated: Motion Concept Lab (Remotion Player) + CapCut for final MP4s.

